        "service_sec1_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "Tailored Premium Web Design",
        "service_sec1_body_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Having a digital presence is no longer just a necessity; it is your brand's most powerful showcase. In my Ankara web design services, I step away from template designs to deliver custom solutions where every pixel is tailored to your brand's vision. Built with Vanilla JS and modern CSS, these websites are entirely free from the performance issues and security vulnerabilities of ready-made systems like WordPress.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Translating your physical prestige into the digital world begins with representing your corporate identity correctly. By using premium typography like Playfair Display, minimalist layouts, and fluid micro-animations, I turn the user journey into a delightful experience. My designs are not just visually stunning; they are fully aligned with Google's search algorithms.</p>\n",
        "service_sec2_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "SEO-Ready Infrastructure & Core Web Vitals",
        "service_sec2_body_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Google directly measures your website's speed and technical health to determine rankings. I place metrics known as Core Web Vitals—LCP (Largest Contentful Paint), FID (First Input Delay), and CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift)—at the center of my development workflow. Bulky websites that take seconds to load cause you to lose potential customers.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">By keeping page load speeds under 1 second, I actively boost your conversion rates. I develop fast, secure, and Google-compliant websites for corporate firms in Ankara's leading business hubs (Ostim, Ivedik, Çankaya, Bilkent) to help them compete globally. Technical SEO is built directly into the foundation.</p>\n",
        "service_sec3_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "Conversion & Growth Oriented UI/UX",
        "service_sec3_body_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">A beautiful and fast website is only successful when it converts visitors into clients or business partners. In my freelance web design services, I craft clear Call-to-Action pathways that make user actions (submitting a form, calling, or emailing) effortless.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">With fully responsive layouts, users get a flawless experience across all viewports—from desktop screens to tablets and mobile phones. Elevate your corporate credibility and sales with a modern UI design that powers your growth strategy.</p>\n",
        "service_sidebar_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n            <li>✓ Custom UI Design</li>\n            <li>✓ Clean Vanilla JS Code</li>\n            <li>✓ SEO-Ready Infrastructure</li>\n            <li>✓ Core Web Vitals Performance</li>\n            <li>✓ Mobile-First Responsiveness</li>\n            <li>✓ SSL Security & Form Integration</li>\n        ",
