        "service_label_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "For Industrial & Production",
        "service_title_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "Industrial & Manufacturing Web Design",
        "service_desc_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "Designing multi-language, product catalog-focused, and premium websites for B2B industrial and manufacturing companies expanding globally.",
        "service_sec1_title_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "Digital Export Gateway for B2B Brands",
        "service_sec1_body_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">For industrial production and manufacturing firms, a website is not just a promotional profile; it is an export gateway opening directly to global markets. The B2B websites I design present the technical specifications, certifications, and product catalogs that international buyers and partners search for in the clearest manner.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">With robust multi-language integration, I optimize your site in languages like English, German, Russian, or Arabic to ensure you rank high in global SEO queries (e.g., 'industrial manufacturing Turkey'). A strong digital presence is the first step in establishing international credibility.</p>\n",
        "service_sec2_title_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "Technical Product Catalogs & Certifications",
        "service_sec2_body_endustriyel-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">For manufacturing firms, technical blueprints, PDF catalogs, and quality standards like ISO/CE are the cornerstones of sales. Having these documents easily downloadable and searchable on the website shortens the decision-making cycles of B2B procurement managers.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">I build clean, logical product catalogs to showcase your entire product families, manufacturing capacity, and machinery assets. Combined with 3D product renders, you can showcase your production power without needing to ship heavy machinery to exhibitions.</p>\n",
