        "service_label_3d-urun-animasyonu": "CGI Visualization",
        "service_title_3d-urun-animasyonu": "Cinematic 3D Product Animation",
        "service_desc_3d-urun-animasyonu": "Showcase your product mechanics, internal details, and aesthetic profiles with photorealistic 3D product animations and CGI renders.",
        "service_sec1_title_3d-urun-animasyonu": "Showcase Products in Uncompromising Detail",
        "service_sec1_body_3d-urun-animasyonu": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Explaining the internal mechanics, micro-details, and complex design of your products is challenging with photography or traditional video. Cinematic 3D product animations eliminate physical limitations, allowing you to present product workflows, cross-section views, and exploded part displays flawlessly.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Utilizing Blender and Substance Painter, I texture and render product materials (plastics, glass, brushed steel, anodized metals) with absolute photorealism (CGI). Wow potential clients at first glance on your website, social media, and exhibitions.</p>\n",
        "service_sec2_title_3d-urun-animasyonu": "The Power of 3D Animations in B2B Sales",
        "service_sec2_body_3d-urun-animasyonu": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">In B2B sales, taking heavy machinery or complex engineering systems to a client's office or setting up expo booths for every client meeting is impossible. A 3D product animation is the most powerful presentation asset your sales team can carry. You can display the internal operation of a machine in seconds on a laptop or tablet.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">I build elegant animations showing the working logic of your product while protecting proprietary technical blueprints. This elevates your marketing impact while safeguarding intellectual property.</p>\n",
